INSERT INTO `story` VALUES (5, '<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"34187474\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/187/474/1715cb92a03120e9bfd6272486d9d894_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626141634&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=2e3131319229f819e6ccc2d2146e3355\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/187/474/1715cb92a03120e9bfd6272486d9d894_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626141634&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=2e3131319229f819e6ccc2d2146e3355\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Keychron is back with another bang for our eighth Kickstarter campaign, the Keychron K7. The K7 is the world’s first ultra-slim 65% layout compact wireless mechanical keyboard, as well as the first low-profile Gateron mechanical keyboard that comes with a hot-swappable option to let you customize your per key typing experience with ease.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"33841211\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/841/211/e19fabee66decec38653a3cac8439ce5_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1623323687&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=ae9e6c9f67c36c2ebbf7f47e72bffac1\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/841/211/e19fabee66decec38653a3cac8439ce5_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1623323687&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=ae9e6c9f67c36c2ebbf7f47e72bffac1\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">We redesigned the low-profile optical switch to deliver a consistent tactile response on the hot-swappable optical version and the reinforced aluminum frame makes the K7 one of the thinnest mechanical keyboards on the market.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"33840948\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/840/948/bec118b5897d04e6a4d69d9c8af62254_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1623321736&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=d996a40a85d0141f043ebd6f3f59c2f6\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/840/948/bec118b5897d04e6a4d69d9c8af62254_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1623321736&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=d996a40a85d0141f043ebd6f3f59c2f6\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">You can connect the K7 with up to 3 devices with a stable Bluetooth 5.1 wireless connection and it\'s compatible with both macOS and Windows. The K7 is packed with all the essential tech features in a 65% layout that’s designed to take up as little space as possible and help you accomplish any task effortlessly.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"33797953\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/797/953/16f789341eda3e2d07cb9fda4ee4fe8c_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1623051937&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=15f69122697c0075b340fe5b2ee5f4f5\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/797/953/16f789341eda3e2d07cb9fda4ee4fe8c_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1623051937&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=15f69122697c0075b340fe5b2ee5f4f5\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"33798311\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-botto