aseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR SUPPORTING THIS CRAZY PROJECT! &nbsp;We can\'t wait to get these printed and to you as soon as possible!&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `story` VALUES (10, '<h1 id=\"h:the-start\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Start</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">When I left the career I loved 4 years ago, I had no idea what was next for me. It sort of felt like walking off of a cliff without knowing whether or not there would be something there to catch me, and while it was super scary and didn\'t make a lot of sense, I had a peace about knowing deep down in my gut that it was the right thing to do. I had this unexplainable sense of peace and excitement in the unknown. Little did I know what was to come. A few months after that \"walking off a cliff\" moment, with some extra time and brain space freed up, I started asking myself the question: what would I do if I could do anything I wanted?&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The answer? Open a coffee truck. I was just as surprised as anyone at that answer, but the more I thought about it, the less surprising it was. First of all, I loved coffee and all that coffee shops had to offer. I loved our community of Modesto and believed it could be a better place to live. I had years of experience growing and leading a team, and I have always felt called to serve people and make them feel seen and cared for. So it was then that Culture Coffee Bar was born. As the idea grew into more than just idea, we started to test the waters and opened up our small little table selling cold brew at our local gym. This was a way to both see if this was a feasible idea, and if I\'m being honest, I needed to prove to myself I could do it. &nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"First Event with Table Set-Up\" data-id=\"34223430\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/223/430/3fc0377e469eec670c6eae9b02689ec5_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626390561&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=d7250a58cb2ab8e543ab5de261e1575a\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/223/430/3fc0377e469eec670c6eae9b02689ec5_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626390561&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=d7250a58cb2ab8e543ab5de261e1575a\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">First Event with Table Set-Up</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Instantly, the business started to grow. We were attracting more and more people and I started to feel like we could actually do this. Then, a couple months in, we got shut down by the health department. We didn\'t know it at the time, but apparently they were unable to issue permits for us to continue running the way we were. This was devastating, but I knew we needed to move forward. I had proven to myself that I could do this and our community had proven that they would show up for us, so we kept walking forward. Our next step was to move forward with building what is currently Culture Coffee Bar.</p><h1 id=\"h:the-trailer\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Trailer</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">In early 2018 we began the process to build a mobile coffee trailer that would become Culture Coffee Bar. We took a 1970 Shasta Camper and had it completely renovated into a mobile coffee shop. Our vision for the trailer was for it to be a vessel to bring the community together and make people feel seen. We wanted to offer an experience that you couldn\'t get anywhere else, one that made you proud of where you lived. We were passionate about offering quality specialty coffee and unique house-made drinks with thought and care put into every menu item. We wanted this to be different than anything else you\'ve ever seen, in the most refreshing way. This vision drove the entire process.</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"The Trailer &quot;before&quot;\" data-id=\"34255936\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/936/c1f373b6ccff924c40fc39bebe8f9a5f_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716631&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=c1b8cb586f8ce7e70cf566c38d9b9c46\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/936/c1f373b6ccff924c40fc39bebe8f9a5f_original.JPG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716631&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=c1b8cb586f8ce7e70cf566c38d9b9c46\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">The Trailer \"before\"</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Making it through the building, permitting and start-up process was one of the hardest things I had ever done, but we made it through and opened at our first event in August of 2018. &nbsp;After that first event, we hit the ground running. We showed up in the community at local events and pop-up shops, hosted our own weekly pop-ups and were invited to participate in some of the most incredible local events. Our community (you guys reading this) kept showing up, day after day. You encouraged us when we were slammed with 1 hour wait times, were always so kind, and you were really the ones who sustained us and allowed us to actually do this thing. &nbsp;Our vision was quickly becoming a reality. We grew our team from a couple friends who just volunteered to help me out because they felt bad that I had no idea what I was doing, to a growing team of 5. Over that first year and a half we continued to grow at a rapid pace, one that many times outpaced our capacity.</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"The Trailer &quot;after&quot;\" data-id=\"34255951\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/951/33d8ee9ad847458eab5557011ffb6066_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716743&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=22575295c5a2d97d0d4f7e5c8612c6f6\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/951/33d8ee9ad847458eab5557011ffb6066_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716743&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=22575295c5a2d97d0d4f7e5c8612c6f6\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">The Trailer \"after\"</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"Some of the Culture Team\" data-id=\"34255961\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/961/48e2a2f835b20efea434742cc788ab70_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716783&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=9998d7e423dbe1f5919def54382d2d60\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/961/48e2a2f835b20efea434742cc788ab70_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716783&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=9998d7e423dbe1f5919def54382d2d60\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">Some of the Culture Team</figcaption></figure></div><h1 id=\"h:the-growth\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Growth</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">At the end of 2019, moving into 2020, we started sensing that we were nearing a point where we could no longer sustain growth at the same pace that we had in our first year of business. At many events we were serving hundreds and hundreds of drinks in a few hour time span. With a single group espresso machine, and a very small space, we can only make so many drinks at once, and a 1 hour wait time for coffee at times was just too much. To help relieve some of those growing pains, we built in additional systems both on the technology side and the process side that allowed us to work more efficiently, which helped significantly.</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"At a pop-up at Get Fit\" data-id=\"34255975\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/975/fd67abea528b6bed1f1897b83ba1e6b4_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716846&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=7417ba07c2ccb8aaaec488d450763d77\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/255/975/fd67abea528b6bed1f1897b83ba1e6b4_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626716846&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=7417ba07c2ccb8aaaec488d450763d77\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">At a pop-up at Get Fit</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Then, the pandemic hit. Devastated again, we knew this would not be the end for us. It took a couple weeks, but we decided to pivot pretty quickly after the lockdown. It was killing us to know that our entire community had everything ripped out from under them with no solid ground to stand on. We wanted to be able to provide some sense of normalcy, something to brighten peoples\' day in a dark time. &nbsp;So we built an entire website with online ordering, and started offering delivery of cold brew. We had no clue what we were doing, and that first delivery route may have taken 10 hours, but like we\'ve done before, we established systems that worked and started delivering 500 cold brews a week for the first couple months of the lockdown. Again, our community showed up. You ordered coffee week after week and helped us sustain this thing through an otherwise really rough time. Two months after the lockdown, we got to re-open at the Modesto Farmer\'s Market. And in 2020, during a pandemic, our business grew another 70% from the prior year. While this growth is incredible, and we\'re continuing to grow in 2021, we just don\'t have the capacity to continue growth at this rate with the size of our current operation. It is clear that it\'s time to take that next step.</p><p><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><h1 id=\"h:the-space\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Space</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Toward the end of 2020, we started the process of negotiating a lease for a brick and mortar space for Culture Coffee Bar, and in May of this year, we signed a lease for a 1900 SF space at 2801 Mchenry Ave. Ste A. in Modesto.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"Front View of Space\" data-id=\"34256006\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/256/006/6f564b9e5b42ebce2764187fae5ff620_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626717039&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=a033261f9f8f73da9ceb91a4d45b2970\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/256/006/6f564b9e5b42ebce2764187fae5ff620_original.jpeg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626717039&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=a033261f9f8f73da9ceb91a4d45b2970\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">Front View of Space</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">&nbsp;We see this space truly becoming the neighborhood coffee shop. We plan to keep moving forward in our mission to serve people by fostering the culture of community that we\'ve already been able to establish on a mobile scale. We want to continue to support other small businesses through collaboration and pop-up events. Ultimately, we want to continue growing our vision of helping the people of Modesto love where they live and have a place where they feel at home.&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">This space was ours from day 1. I mean, not on paper or anything, but we just KNEW it would be ours. The space used to be the home to Sidelines, and has been empty for many, many years. While it may not be the most aesthetically pleasing space, it holds a ton of value to us. That career I left years ago, the one where I was walking off of a cliff into nothing-ness? That job was at a place I loved (and still love), and it just so happens to be right next door, Get Fit. Get Fit was where I first really dove into the idea of creating community, of building something bigger than myself and where we started with a table set up just outside the door. You see what I mean when I say it was meant for us? This space is also in MY neighborhood. I don\'t think you can get any more meant to be than building a neighborhood coffee shop in your own neighborhood. This space is a reminder of how God can use ugly, broken-down things, and broken people and bring them back to life to use them to do some pretty amazing things.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"Current Inside of Space\" data-id=\"34223952\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/223/952/2a6e1cdb51e3b2532d7d328dc256312a_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626394940&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=1b69846a69368e9f5b619ea7fd4b2016\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/223/952/2a6e1cdb51e3b2532d7d328dc256312a_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626394940&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=1b69846a69368e9f5b619ea7fd4b2016\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">Current Inside of Space</figcaption></figure></div><h1 id=\"h:the-plan\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Plan</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">We will be taking this 1900 SF space and breathing new life into it. We will have indoor/outdoor seating and plenty of space to hang out with friends, sit and work, or dive into a new book. We will be updating the exterior with new windows, and completely re-building the interior from the ground up. We will continue to offer all of your Culture faves with an expanded food and drink menu. We have been working on plans for a couple of months and have loved thinking about all of the life that will happen within these walls. As far as the current state of the project, we have finished demo of the space and are starting construction. We plan to open our doors late 2021 and cannot wait to share this space with you, our Culture fam, and serve all of our neighbors. We plan to be a staple in our community for years to come and are so thankful to you for helping us do so.</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"Our Plan for the Space\" data-id=\"34223961\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/223/961/a2faa073c4bc177c1cb083d1df15c9ce_original.PNG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626395009&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=5e79fd95989e7038b86b998195d6d0d9\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/223/961/a2faa073c4bc177c1cb083d1df15c9ce_original.PNG?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626395009&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=5e79fd95989e7038b86b998195d6d0d9\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">Our Plan for the Space</figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">`</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"Early Design Renderings\" data-id=\"34256117\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/256/117/79642c6b6ad37734d557199025b3f137_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626717569&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=068a6e2990328b5d3890b8dd2e604367\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/256/117/79642c6b6ad37734d557199025b3f137_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626717569&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=068a6e2990328b5d3890b8dd2e604367\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><figcaption class=\"px2\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); padding-right: 1.2rem !important; padding-left: 1.2rem !important;\">Early Design Renderings</figcaption></figure></div><p><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><h1 id=\"h:the-funds\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Funds</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">As a family, we are all in on this project. We are using all of our resources, along with some Tenant Improvement funds to get 90% of this project taken care of. That is where you come in. We need help getting that last 10% of the way. From the beginning, we knew this is something we wouldn\'t want to do alone. We are building this for you, our community, and want you to feel like you\'re a part of something bigger. Your generosity will help us steward this business well, so it can continue to be sustainable for a very long time.&nbsp;</p><h1 id=\"h:the-rewards\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Rewards</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">We have set up some really fun rewards to reward you for your generosity. Through this Kickstarter, we are offering coffee memberships to Culture! These will only be available through this kickstarter and will be a fun way to pre-purchase your coffee, while helping to build this beautiful community space. Check out all of the details in the \"Rewards\" section of this site.</p>', NULL);
INSERT INTO `story` VALUES (11, '<div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"34231506\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/231/506/014db12bd5c1005c5608a0f635b87c8d_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626457771&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=1003cb2fd4e12e7122a91ab5e9c4f93f\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/231/506/014db12bd5c1005c5608a0f635b87c8d_original.jpg?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1626457771&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;q=92&amp;s=1003cb2fd4e12e7122a91ab5e9c4f93f\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">With the explosion of media over the last few years, it seems that the word&nbsp;<span class=\"text-italic\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">film&nbsp;</span></span>has been replaced with&nbsp;<span class=\"text-italic\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">content</span></span>. That we as an audience are force-fed passable movies solely created to keep us in the&nbsp;algorithm. We watch it once and never think about it again.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">But what about those films that stick with you? Those films that come to mind when you mention the word&nbsp;<span class=\"text-italic\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">cinema</span></span>. That is what we aim to do with our short film&nbsp;<span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">Panorama.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">In order to accomplish this, we need you our&nbsp;<span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">community</span>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Our hope, is that by giving you the opportunity to be involved, we cultivate a larger community around this film.</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"33945647\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/945/647/00df59a1d758927fd93a29272b8a803d_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1624140577&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=ebfc1182ca594ddb7973ee24c38c016f\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/033/945/647/00df59a1d758927fd93a29272b8a803d_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1624140577&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=ebfc1182ca594ddb7973ee24c38c016f\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><h1 id=\"h:what-is-panorama\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">What is Panorama?</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><span class=\"text-italic\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">Panorama</span>&nbsp;is a 15 minute short film that explores our dreams, memories, and reality through&nbsp;the relationship of a Mother and Son that stars&nbsp;<span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">Shane Paul McGhie</span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">Karimah Westbrook.</span>&nbsp;Upon completion, we will be sending our film to the&nbsp;<span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">2022 Sundance Film Festival.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">Our story takes place&nbsp;two months after the unexpected passing of Sam\'s mother. While leaving a party with his girlfriend Danielle, a tragic event takes place that catapults Sam into a Near Death Experience where his Mother takes him through every chapter of his life.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">With an incredible cast, top-level producers including several current and former NFL players, an emerging director, and&nbsp;<span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">YOU</span>, Panorama will be set for a major film festival campaign this Fall.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">TARGET GOAL: $10,000</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">With hitting our Target Goal we will be able take care of our post-production.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">STRETCH GOAL: $15,000</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">With our 15k Stretch Goal, we will be able to afford a high profile song for our opening scene and higher quality meals for our crew.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">STRETCH GOAL: $20,000</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">With our 20k Stretch Goal, we will be able to cover our festival submissions, private screenings, and for marketing during our Fall Campaign.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"34170361\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/170/361/e9bb54a1f983edb53ccd06d0ec52a3a1_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1625986520&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=316bbe970e950cb89b63be3ac8727e0d\" src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/170/361/e9bb54a1f983edb53ccd06d0ec52a3a1_original.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.2&amp;w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1625986520&amp;auto=format&amp;frame=1&amp;lossless=true&amp;s=316bbe970e950cb89b63be3ac8727e0d\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"></figure></div><h1 id=\"h:the-funding\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">The Funding&nbsp;</span></h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">This Kickstarter will raise the funds to finish the financing of Panorama. Things like renting gear, feeding our crew, and post-production. Through private investments, we are nearly at the finish line, but we need our community to take us through the finish line. We want to open this up not only to involve you, but to also give an opportunity to share in the success of this film. We want to inspire our fellow filmmakers by not only telling truthful stories, but showing them that there is a support system to uplift young artists in following their dreams.&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p><h1 id=\"h:the-rewards\" class=\"page-anchor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 50px; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\">The Rewards</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><span class=\"bold\" style=\"border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\">$20</span>&nbsp;- Thank you for helping us out, every dollar is appreciated!&nbsp;</p><div class=\"template asset\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt-text=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-id=\"34188202\" style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Maison Neue Book&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);\"><figure style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: inherit;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"fit lazyloaded\" data-src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/034/188/202/f5b7fb7679bcd28a5f9c8ba06a4cdb68_original.png